<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OnlineBooking Pro</title>
<style>
/* ===== RESET ===== */
* {margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box;}
body {font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background: #0f0f0f; color: #fff; line-height:1.6;}
a {text-decoration:none;}
button {cursor:pointer;}

/* ===== HEADER ===== */
header {position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); padding:20px 50px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; z-index:100;}
header .logo {font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:#00ff99;}
header nav a {margin-left:25px; color:#fff; font-weight:500; transition:0.3s;}
header nav a:hover {color:#00ff99;}

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero {height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center; text-align:center; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#111,#000); padding:0 20px;}
.hero h1 {font-size:60px; margin-bottom:20px;}
.hero p {font-size:20px; max-width:600px; margin-bottom:30px; color:#aaa;}
.hero .btn {background:#00ff99; color:#000; padding:15px 40px; font-weight:bold; border-radius:10px; transition:0.3s;}
.hero .btn:hover {transform:scale(1.05);}

/* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
section {padding:100px 50px;}
section h2 {text-align:center; font-size:40px; margin-bottom:50px; color:#00ff99;}
.cards {display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:20px; justify-content:center;}
.card {background:#1a1a1a; padding:25px; border-radius:15px; width:300px; text-align:center; transition:0.3s;}
.card:hover {transform:translateY(-10px); box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,255,153,0.3);}
.card h3 {margin-bottom:15px;}
.card p {color:#aaa;}

/* ===== SERVICES ===== */
#services .card {cursor:default;}

/* ===== SCHEDULE / TIMETABLE ===== */
#schedule .card {background:#111; border:1px solid #00ff99; padding:20px;}
.schedule-day {margin-bottom:20px;}
.schedule-day h4 {margin-bottom:10px; color:#00ff99;}
.schedule-day ul {list-style:none;}
.schedule-day ul li {padding:5px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #222;}
.schedule-day ul li:last-child {border:none;}

/* ===== FORM ===== */
.form {display:flex; flex-direction:column; max-width:500px; margin:auto; gap:15px;}
.form input, .form textarea, .form button {padding:15px; border-radius:10px; border:none; font-size:16px;}
.form input, .form textarea {background:#1a1a1a; color:#fff;}
.form button {background:#00ff99; color:#000; font-weight:bold; transition:0.3s;}
.form button:hover {transform:scale(1.05);}

/* ===== CONTACTS ===== */
.contact-link {display:block; margin:20px auto 0 auto; background:#00ff99; color:#000; padding:20px 0; border-radius:15px; font-weight:bold; width:80%; text-align:center; font-size:20px; transition:0.3s;}
.contact-link:hover {transform:scale(1.05);}

/* ===== POPUP ===== */
.popup {position:fixed; bottom:30px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); background:#00ff99; color:#000; padding:20px 30px; border-radius:10px; display:none; z-index:999; font-weight:bold;}

/* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
.fade-in {opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); animation:fadeIn 1s forwards;}
@keyframes fadeIn {to {opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">OnlineBooking Pro</div>
<nav>
<a href="#hero">Главная</a>
<a href="#services">Преимущества</a>
<a href="#schedule">Услуги</a>
<a href="#form">Запись</a>
<a href="#contacts">Контакты</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="hero">
<h1 class="fade-in">Быстрая запись к мастеру</h1>
<p class="fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.3s;">Записывайся онлайн за 1 минуту. Удобно, безопасно, эффективно.</p>
<a class="btn fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.6s;" href="#form">Записаться</a>
</section>

<section id="services">
<h2>Преимущества</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.1s;"><h3>Онлайн запись</h3><p>Не нужно звонить – всё через сайт</p></div>
<div class="card fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.2s;"><h3>Напоминания</h3><p>СМС и Telegram уведомления о записи</p></div>
<div class="card fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.3s;"><h3>Безопасность</h3><p>Ваши данные защищены и конфиденциальны</p></div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="schedule">
<h2>Услуги и расписание</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.1s;">
<div class="schedule-day">
<h4>Понедельник</h4>
<ul>
<li>Маникюр: 10:00 – 18:00</li>
<li>Массаж: 12:00 – 20:00</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="schedule-day">
<h4>Вторник</h4>
<ul>
<li>Маникюр: 10:00 – 18:00</li>
<li>Массаж: 12:00 – 20:00</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card fade-in" style="animation-delay:0.2s;">
<div class="schedule-day">
<h4>Среда</h4>
<ul>
<li>Маникюр: 10:00 – 18:00</li>
<li>Массаж: 12:00 – 20:00</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="schedule-day">
<h4>Четверг</h4>
<ul>
<li>Маникюр: 10:00 – 18:00</li>
<li>Массаж: 12:00 – 20:00</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="form">
<h2>Оставить заявку</h2>
<form class="form">
<input placeholder="Имя" required>
<input placeholder="Контакт (Telegram, WhatsApp, Email)" required>
<textarea placeholder="Что нужно" required></textarea>
<button>Отправить заявку</button>
</form>
</section>

<section id="contacts">
<h2>Контакты</h2>
<a class="contact-link" href="https://t.me/vova_terminator" target="_blank">Связаться с нами</a>
</section>

<div class="popup">Заявка отправлена 🚀</div>

<script>
document.querySelector('.form').addEventListener('submit',function(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    document.querySelector('.popup').style.display='block';
    setTimeout(()=>{document.querySelector('.popup').style.display='none';},2000);
    this.reset();
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
